MGPL RES Privacy Policy

Effective Date: 08/06/2023

Introduction
Welcome to Myforklift. This Privacy Policy aims to provide you with a clear understanding of how we collect, use, and disclose personal information and data from users of the Myforklift mobile application. By utilizing our App, you explicitly consent to the practices outlined in this Privacy Policy.

Information We Collect
(a) Personal Information:

We collect specific data to enhance your experience and facilitate efficient team management. The data we collect includes your location, as it enables your manager to track your current work location. Additionally, we gather your usage history to allow supervision and optimization of team performance.
(b) Non-Personal Information:

In addition to personal data, we also gather non-personal information that does not directly identify you. This may include, but is not limited to, device information, app usage data, and action histories stored by user name for analytical purposes.

How We Use Your Information
We utilize the information we collect for various purposes, including:

(a) Providing and Improving Our Services:

Our primary objective is to deliver a seamless and enhanced user experience. We leverage your information to operate, maintain, and optimize our App's features and functionality, ensuring that it adds maximum value to your team.

(c) Tracking Usage and Assessing Impact:

Understanding how you interact with our App is crucial for continuous improvement. By analyzing your usage patterns, we can evaluate the App's effectiveness in assisting you with your daily responsibilities.

(d) Analyzing App Usage:

To enhance performance and user satisfaction, we carefully analyze user behavior and app usage patterns, implementing insights to deliver a better user experience.

Data Sharing and Disclosure
(a) Third-Party Service Providers:

To ensure seamless App operation and improvement, we may share your information with trusted third-party service providers. These providers are contractually bound by confidentiality agreements, ensuring that your information remains safeguarded and is not used for any other purposes.

(b) Legal Requirements:

We are committed to upholding legal obligations and protecting our rights. Therefore, we may access, preserve, and disclose your information if required by law or in good faith belief that such actions are necessary to comply with legal obligations, safeguard our rights, or detect and prevent fraudulent or security-related issues.

(c) Business Transfers:

In the event of a merger, acquisition, or sale of all or part of our assets, your information may be transferred as part of the transaction. Rest assured, we will notify you of any such changes in ownership or control of your personal information.

Your Choices and Rights
(a) Access and Update:

We respect your right to access, correct, or update your personal information through your account settings.

(b) Data Retention:

Your information will be retained only as long as necessary to fulfill the purposes outlined in this Privacy Policy or as required by applicable law.

Opt-Out:
You have the option to opt-out of receiving promotional communications from us. Please follow the instructions provided in the communication to exercise this right.

Data Security
While we implement reasonable security measures to protect your information from unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction, please be aware that no method of transmission over the internet or electronic storage is entirely foolproof.

Children's Privacy
Our App is not intended for children under the age of [the age limit defined by your applicable data protection laws]. We do not knowingly collect or solicit personal information from children. If we learn that we have inadvertently collected personal information from a child, we will promptly delete it.

Changes to this Privacy Policy
We may periodically update this Privacy Policy. Any changes will be effective upon posting the revised policy on this page. We encourage you to review this Privacy Policy periodically for any updates.

Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns regarding this Privacy Policy or our data practices, please feel free to contact us at service@mgpl.ma.

By utilizing the Myforklift App, you explicitly consent to the terms and conditions set forth in this Privacy Policy.
